The paper deals with decision making and decision support systems, which are typically studied in the fields of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data science (cs.DS). The focus on selecting a preferred subset of a given set of items based on their attributes suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the fields of machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper's emphasis on computing an optimal subset given a preference specification suggests that it may also be relevant to the field of databases (cs.DB).
